creator: USA2GEORGIA
descriptionHtml:
The ability to control your packages is now at your fingertips. Robust and user-friendly USA2GEORGIA app allows you to:

• Check you package status
• Declare package
• Upload package invoices
• Make payments
• Access unique bar code to obtain your package instantly at our office.

You can also request delivery service, forward your package to a locker, check package arrival times and access our FAQ. And you can do all of this from your iPhone or android phone!

The application is available to all USA2GEORGIA customers as we continue building robust and convenient company to serve our customers shipping needs.

For feedback please reach out to: sales@usa2georgia.com
descriptionShort: We simplify your purchase shipping process.
